  "body": "\r\n**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nProxyd should have on option to verify a config is valid without having to start the server process.\r\n\r\n**Describe the solution you'd like**\r\nSomething like `proxyd checkconfig --config <PATH-TO-FILE>`\r\nProxyd should use exit code 1 if the configuration is invalid.\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nIf proxyd is restarted with an invalid configuration the service will be down until the situation is fixed.\r\n\r\n",
